        <characteristic name="Abilities" typeId="492d-1f80-b777-26f2">Strikes last, Any model wounded but not killed cannot attack until end of next Assault Phase, Vehicles suffer an automatic &quot;crew shaken&quot; result if hit.</characteristic>
